Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.02,0:02:27.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使你死在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.89,0:02:29.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也一定会转世
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.48,0:02:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转世回到…我们家里来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.64,0:02:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转世这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.44,0:02:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真是假  我马上就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就先去确认真假啰  大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.09,0:02:51.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.96,0:02:58.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昌  昌弘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.62,0:02:59.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.94,0:03:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  可恶  可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.33,0:03:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这群混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.65,0:03:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧给我结束吧  混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.14,0:03:19.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙  是瞄准装甲缝隙来打的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.68,0:03:22.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我渐渐明白这东西的用法了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:29.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事  真是奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我的心情会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.54,0:03:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:34.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.29,0:03:37.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑啊  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.93,0:03:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你其实很享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.59,0:03:43.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,享受杀人的快感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.02,0:03:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.68,0:03:53.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是  好想…好想杀死你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:04:01.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在…享受？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.04,0:04:06.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:12.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正这家伙  死有余辜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.31,0:05:57.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜您
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.85,0:06:00.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  真是个久违的好消息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.73,0:06:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下柏德文卿也安心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天你们就好好放松一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.70,0:06:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.19,0:06:12.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊兹纳里奥大人将庶子用得恰到好处呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.78,0:06:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  迎娶了柏德文家的掌上明珠后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.38,0:06:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在七星家族内的地位也就更加稳固了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.12,0:06:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  净聚了些低俗之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.70,0:06:27.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就随他们说去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.35,0:06:28.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦克吉利斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:32.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  方便的话可否赏脸小叙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.17,0:06:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离你告别单身还有点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.53,0:06:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里我就当没看见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:40.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  真是惹人怜爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.43,0:06:43.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直像洋娃娃一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.77,0:06:51.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦奇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.78,0:07:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是为了家族  但这也太操之过急了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.26,0:07:06.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方可是刚脱离尿布的小孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.70,0:07:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  麦克吉利斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.28,0:07:29.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不去跳舞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.82,0:07:30.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跳不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.79,0:07:34.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我…还是个小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.19,0:07:40.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能像那样和麦奇跳贴面舞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:47.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦奇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.64,0:07:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  跳舞吧  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.31,0:07:53.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.62,0:07:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是被人看见了  会笑话我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.01,0:07:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔米莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.55,0:08:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有谁敢笑话你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:02.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不会放过他的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.56,0:08:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是比这里任何人都美丽的淑女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.48,0:08:12.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦奇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.17,0:08:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚是个特别的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就忘记一切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.55,0:08:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也忘记接下来即将开始的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.71,0:08:25.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞至天明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.67,0:08:30.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这四周还藏着那帮死老头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都小心点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.60,0:08:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.83,0:08:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但丁  总共就这些人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.98,0:08:36.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:38.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,团长  他们…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.57,0:08:47.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火星虽然不算什么好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:49.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但总比这里强
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.82,0:08:52.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总部的运营也逐渐稳定了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.61,0:08:54.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃饭还有汤喝喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.32,0:08:56.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,团长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.67,0:08:58.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟大哥说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.95,0:09:01.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙就交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:03.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.70,0:09:04.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「交给我们」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:05.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,团长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.27,0:09:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到刚才  我们还在和你们对战呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.56,0:09:13.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.60,0:09:15.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是工作需要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.13,0:09:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就没办法了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.34,0:09:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.81,0:09:21.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是因为想做  才这么做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.40,0:09:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.14,0:09:27.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前什么都没想过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.10,0:09:29.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己什么也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.41,0:09:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.15,0:09:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类之屑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在宇宙中诞生  不惧怕在宇宙中逝去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.59,0:09:42.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高傲不屈  是被选中的家伙们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.20,0:09:48.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁华团  欢迎你们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,团长  谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.05,0:10:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,篠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪下达命令的我不中用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.54,0:10:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才让那些家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:23.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.63,0:10:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话  还不如让我去死更好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:29.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  篠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.49,0:10:33.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话  对他们太失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.38,0:10:41.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.54,0:10:44.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赔偿金我要一分不少地收了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.74,0:10:46.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布鲁克·卡巴扬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.26,0:10:49.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名濑·塔宾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.95,0:10:52.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要什么呢  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.98,0:10:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.87,0:10:59.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一艘船  以及所有的机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.85,0:11:00.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.07,0:11:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你怎么不去抢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.67,0:11:06.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愿意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.38,0:11:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你的肉切下来卖了也行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.85,0:11:10.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然脂肪有点多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.79,0:11:12.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但勉强还能喂狗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.93,0:11:18.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按照计划  接下来将前往殖民地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.32,0:11:21.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布鲁沃茨持有的资产
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.67,0:11:25.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有两艘船  能修的机动战士有十台
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.72,0:11:26.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.01,0:11:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是些装甲异常厚实的机动战士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.09,0:11:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  大多内部都没什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.42,0:11:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是那台叫古辛的  可有些年头了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.58,0:11:38.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么处理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.82,0:11:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把机体交由铁华团…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.75,0:11:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  全部变卖掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.25,0:11:48.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了昭弘弟弟的机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.38,0:11:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不能用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.53,0:11:53.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是  昭弘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.14,0:11:55.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.40,0:11:56.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估计还闷在房间里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.52,0:12:00.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟弟弟死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.02,0:12:04.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葬礼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.44,0:12:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,办个葬礼怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.59,0:12:08.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葬礼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.92,0:12:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.94,0:12:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我出生的殖民地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:14.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是办葬礼为死者送行的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让灵魂回到该去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.74,0:12:20.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后顺利地投胎转世
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.16,0:12:23.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么啊  太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.48,0:12:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得挺好的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:30.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葬礼在过去貌似是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:32.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说通过举行葬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.28,0:12:37.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还能让死者的魂魄忘掉生前的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:38.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘掉痛苦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.06,0:12:39.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.85,0:12:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.93,0:12:42.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,篠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.62,0:12:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…的话  想举行葬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能让他们忘记些许痛苦的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.03,0:12:54.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想拜托大家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.61,0:12:56.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昭弘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.96,0:13:00.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么定了的话  我们也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:03.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也得去通知大家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.05,0:13:05.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.33,0:13:08.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就回渔火了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.53,0:13:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我也回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像不太赞成啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:21.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话  我不是很理解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:25.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么灵魂投胎转世之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.14,0:13:27.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些先死去的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正死后就能见到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.51,0:13:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有那个工夫举办葬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.13,0:13:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不如花时间想想  今后该怎么活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:40.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是…你自己那么想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.74,0:13:46.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是这里所有人  都能接受同伴死去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.54,0:13:51.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,举办葬礼  也是为了活着的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.20,0:13:57.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让他们接受  重要的人的死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.35,0:14:02.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是高高在上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.09,0:14:03.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大妈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.14,0:14:05.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能听见喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.44,0:14:07.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.84,0:14:15.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,举办葬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.22,0:14:15.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.44,0:14:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我不是很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.30,0:14:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟其他人也说一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.33,0:14:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  三日月
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:31.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然三日月回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.44,0:14:34.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那句「太好了」真是说不出口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.95,0:14:37.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.09,0:14:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  三日月还是回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.93,0:14:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  说到葬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.80,0:14:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是有花的话  还能稍微好看点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.26,0:14:57.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个想法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.18,0:14:59.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:15:00.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么想法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（送葬）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.28,0:15:06.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能把这个也放进去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.78,0:15:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:12.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样站在这里  有种微妙的感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.99,0:15:13.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.74,0:15:19.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.82,0:15:21.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.73,0:15:22.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥尔加
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.57,0:15:23.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.69,0:15:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高木  已经不痛了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.12,0:15:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.77,0:15:31.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  大家都祈祷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.08,0:15:39.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祈祷我们死去同伴的灵魂  能够回到应归之处
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.24,0:15:42.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够好好地投胎转世吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.78,0:16:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备吊唁礼炮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.06,0:16:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣炮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.10,0:16:16.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.19,0:16:19.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.80,0:16:21.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开花啦  开花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.36,0:16:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.36,0:16:26.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么弄的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:28.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔  这个炮弹是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.53,0:16:31.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔  这个是用了推进剂的氢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.57,0:16:33.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我稍微做了点小加工
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.62,0:16:35.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是这家伙出的主意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.57,0:16:37.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是山木啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:40.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:42.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.71,0:16:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就没了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.81,0:16:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能一直开着就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.04,0:16:52.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:16:59.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是想不开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.87,0:17:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活着的时候  就快活一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.94,0:17:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为无聊的事情而发笑  打闹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.99,0:17:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失的时候就是一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.32,0:17:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.53,0:17:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓葬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.48,0:17:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是为了能让活着的人尽情哭泣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.57,0:17:24.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  至少今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:24.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.42,0:17:28.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在送走风光的伙伴的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.63,0:17:31.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不想让自己显得没出息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.53,0:17:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是一群傻孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.91,0:17:51.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚好安静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.73,0:17:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.37,0:17:56.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.78,0:17:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱德  怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.03,0:18:00.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他哭得停不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.11,0:18:03.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵得其他人睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.31,0:18:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈…呜呜…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.98,0:18:09.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来  我抱抱你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.28,0:18:12.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了  反正阿特拉也没胸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.78,0:18:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.86,0:18:15.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要抱的话  我选弗米坦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:17.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.37,0:18:18.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗米坦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.33,0:18:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.78,0:18:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  在这在这  山木
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.11,0:18:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,篠  你等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.53,0:18:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.23,0:18:37.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些冰花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.32,0:18:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  这么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.94,0:18:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我死的时候  也要给我多放几发喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.70,0:18:48.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.53,0:18:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个礼花  工艺挺复杂的  还费钱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:56.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是葬礼这么频繁  我可受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:18:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈  说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.82,0:19:02.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起啦  我就是想道个谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.49,0:19:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  这样买卖手续就完成了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.83,0:19:10.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.64,0:19:11.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.45,0:19:13.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:16.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不光是战利品  还有葬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.18,0:19:18.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要挂在心上  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.07,0:19:19.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.40,0:19:21.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿米达
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.03,0:19:28.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…你们怎么突然就亲热起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.42,0:19:31.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.65,0:19:34.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死亡率高的年份  出生率也会上升
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.94,0:19:35.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.81,0:19:38.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为人类会自动判断要留下后代啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.77,0:19:43.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话  身边的女人看起来就会非常可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:44.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都很可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.00,0:19:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是当然  比平常还要可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原…原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.65,0:19:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  你想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:19:58.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙可以给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.20,0:20:00.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.46,0:20:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说你要驾驶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.84,0:20:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葬礼的时候  我想起了死去的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.27,0:20:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是跟没怎么说过话的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.81,0:20:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也会有些无聊的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.55,0:20:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是跟昌弘  就只有童年的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.63,0:20:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最新的  最深刻的回忆  却是他的死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.08,0:20:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那至少  从今往后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.15,0:20:28.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要跟他的回忆在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.63,0:20:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.98,0:20:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你其实很享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.68,0:20:37.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,享受杀人的快感
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.11,0:20:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.64,0:20:45.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明平时那么开朗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.61,0:20:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葬礼的时候  也为了冰礼花而手舞足蹈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.30,0:20:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也无可厚非
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:52.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们还是孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.15,0:20:56.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会无意识地将很多纠葛埋于心底
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.58,0:20:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些扭曲会在某些时候显现出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.04,0:21:02.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无意识地…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.08,0:21:09.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐  差不多该休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.77,0:21:12.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想再留一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.60,0:21:20.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁华团
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.62,0:21:25.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被赋予「不谢之花」之名的他们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.95,0:21:27.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.75,0:21:30.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三日月
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.16,0:21:32.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你睡不着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.76,0:21:34.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  就是有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.80,0:21:37.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.35,0:21:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  啊  那我就不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.59,0:21:44.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三日月  你是在发抖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.60,0:21:45.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的  为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.74,0:21:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天有点奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.36,0:21:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许三日月也会有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.59,0:22:00.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无意识压制着的强烈情感
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.23,0:22:10.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.87,0:22:12.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.81,0:22:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚弗米坦对小孩子们这样做…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.63,0:22:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话会稍稍安心一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.03,0:22:23.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…那个  对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.59,0:22:32.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.63,0:22:36.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么  干什么  干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.54,0:22:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我觉得你很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.19,0:22:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  你讨厌这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.16,0:22:45.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是讨厌不讨厌的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.86,0:22:48.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这之前  这种事情是要…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.02,0:23:07.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被加拉尔号角压榨的民众们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.89,0:23:11.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,焦急期待着美丽革命家的登场
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.63,0:23:17.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.34,0:23:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装饰克迪莉娅·蓝那·博斯坦汀之死的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.65,0:23:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是殖民地了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.31,0:24:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死  团长那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.48,0:24:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是「小鬼小鬼」的叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.34,0:24:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又不会像那群孩子一样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.63,0:24:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动不动就想妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.94,0:24:10.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然伤心的事情有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.95,0:24:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  我绝对不会哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.14,0:24:18.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  弗米坦小姐的拥抱  感觉很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.43,0:24:22.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集  机动战士高达  铁血的孤儿
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.95,0:24:25.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第十四话  承载希望之船
